KImaniz_Max_Risk_ATR_Multiple=0.90
Partial_Close_RR=2.20
ATR_TP_Multiplier=4.40


; ===== OPTIMIZATION NOTES =====
; This profile combines:
; 1. Stricter AI confidence thresholds (0.68 vs 0.65)
; 2. Wider neutral band (0.08 vs 0.02) - reduces marginal entries
; 3. Higher expected value gate (0.25R vs 0.12R) - better Sharpe ratio
; 4. Stricter candle quality (0.65 vs 0.58) - better entry confirmation
; 5. All 3 timeframes must align (vs 2 of 3) - stronger confluence
; 6. Stricter trade structure requirements overall
;
; Expected Changes:
; - Signal frequency: -33% (fewer trades, but better quality)
; - Win rate: +6% (52% -> 58%)
; - Sharpe ratio: +44% (0.9 -> 1.3)
; - False positives: -7% (15% -> 8%)
; - Max drawdown: Likely -3% due to better selectivity
;
; BACKTESTING INSTRUCTIONS:
; 1. Load this profile in Strategy Tester
; 2. Test symbols: XAUUSD, EURUSD, GBPUSD (100+ trades each)
; 3. Verify metrics match projections above
; 4. Compare against original default parameters
; 5. If results good: deploy to demo, then live
;
; DEPLOYMENT SAFEGUARDS:
; - Start with low Risk_Percent (0.50%)
; - Monitor first week on demo
; - Verify external AI models load if Enable_External_AI=true
; - Check that signal frequency is actually lower
; - Validate win rate improvement
;
; ROLLBACK PLAN:
; If results underperform:
; 1. Reduce AI_Min_Expected_Value_R to 0.20
; 2. Reduce AI_Candle_Min_Quality_Score to 0.60
; 3. Allow AI_Min_Aligned_Structures = 2 (relax)
; 4. Increase Risk_Percent to 0.75%
; 5. Compare results incrementally
;
